snippet.title: Super Cane Magic ZERO (SCMZ) Launch trailer (Europe)
snippet.description:
Super Cane Magic ZERO is a hilarious and irreverent Action-RPG featuring a couch co-op Story Mode and a frantic Arena Mode, both for up to 4 players! It’s fun alone – and even more of a blast with friends! Eat anything you find or throw it to your enemies, believe in all sort of absurd things and become unstoppable!

Find Super Cane Magic ZERO on Nintendo Switch, Steam, Humble Store and Playstation 4!
Switch
https://www.nintendo.co.uk/Games/Nintendo-Switch-download-software/Super-Cane-Magic-ZERO-1549855.html
Steam
https://store.steampowered.com/…/3364…/Super_Cane_Magic_ZERO

https://store.playstation.com/en-gb/product/EP5688-CUSA14968_00-SCMZ000000000001
